    "The suggested model also has certain drawbacks.",
    "The model can only be trained using high-frequency data on electricity consumption, which restricts its ability to capture the minutest electricity consumption trends.",
    "Its accuracy was also reduced as a result, more cases of misclassification occur.",
    "Furthermore, there is no method for tweaking the hyper parameters, so it can take much computing time.",
    "In the future, we will improve its performance by using the minimum frequency dataset and decreasing the delay in identifying electricity theft in the CNGC dataset."
